reviews.title: High priced but worth it.
reviews.comment: All and all good songs but I wish the lyrics could be translated however the quality is good and u cant find these anywhere elsa.

reviews.comment: Disappointed..  I really am.. The music is what I expected of Miku, AWESOME.. But it doesn\'t sync with my actual music. I don\'t what to have to skip between this app & my actual music player every time I want to listen to a different Vocaloid song. Please fix..  :(
